## LUT word ##

+---------+---------+------+
| 15 - 12 | 11 - 1  | 0    |
+---------+---------+------+
| TYPE    | COMMAND | STOP |
+---------+---------+------+

## Type A command ##

+--------+-------+---+-------+---+
| 11 - 8 | 7 - 4 | 3 | 2 - 1 | 0 |
+--------+-------+---+-------+---+
| OPC1   | OPC2  | D | A     | B |
+--------+-------+---+-------+---+

- OP1:
	Arith. operation 2nd opcode

- OP1:
	Arith. operation 3rd opcode
	
- D:
	1: r0
	0: rD

- A:
	00: rA
	01: rB
	10: rD
	11: r0
	
- B:
	1: r0
	0: rB
	
## Type I command ##

+--------+-------+---+-------+---+
| 11 - 6 | 5 - 4 | 3 | 2 - 1 | 0 |
+--------+-------+---+-------+---+
| OPC0   | I     | D | A     | R |
+--------+-------+---+-------+---+

- OPC0:
	Instruction opcode
	
- I:
        00: Original immediate
        01: Zero immediate
        10: Custom immediate
        11: Reserved
	
- D:
	1: r0
	0: rD

- A:
	00: rA
	01: rB
	10: rD
	11: r0
	
## Type M command ##

+--------+-------+---+-------+---+
| 11 - 6 | 5 - 4 | 3 | 2 - 1 | 0 |
+--------+-------+---+-------+---+
| OPC0   | I     | R | A     | B |
+--------+-------+---+-------+---+

- OPC0:
	Instruction opcode

- I:
        00: Original immediate
        01: Zero immediate
        10: Custom immediate
        11: Reserved

- A:
	00: rA
	01: rB
	10: rD
	11: r0

- B:
	1: r0
	0: rB
